snippet.title: Relics of Gods: Showtime of Heroes
snippet.description: MOBA for mobile! Relics of Gods is a 3D turn-based strategy mobile game with 15 races, over 50 playable heroes, and 1 massive fantasy tale. Coming soon for mobile.  Learn more at http://rog.seasungames.com
